{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:26:00.298Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Self-supervised learning"},{"type":"text","text":" is a machine learning technique where the model "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"creates its own labels from unlabeled data"},{"type":"text","text":" and then learns using those automatically generated labels, combining aspects of supervised and unsupervised learning."}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Simple definition (Stanford):"},{"type":"text","text":" “Self-Supervised Learning is a training method where an AI model "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"teaches itself"},{"type":"text","text":" by creating its own puzzles from raw data and then trying to solve them.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For example:\n- In language: predict the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"missing word"},{"type":"text","text":" in a sentence\n- In images: predict which "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"pieces belong together"},{"type":"text","text":" or reconstruct a corrupted image"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Core idea: learning from data without human labels"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"In self-supervised learning:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You start with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"unlabeled data"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., all text on the internet, raw images)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You design a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"pretext task"},{"type":"text","text":" that uses the data’s structure to create labels automatically:"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- “Given the first part of this sentence, predict the next word” - “Given this part of an image, predict the rest”\n3. The model is trained "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"like a supervised learner"},{"type":"text","text":", but the labels are "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"self-generated"},{"type":"text","text":" from the data itself, not provided by humans\n4. The model learns essential features and relationships in the data to solve these self-generated tasks"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This allows models to be trained on "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"massive unlabeled datasets"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., all the text on the internet) without expensive human annotation."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Self-supervised learning in Generative AI"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Self-supervised learning is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"dominant paradigm"},{"type":"text","text":" for training modern "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generative AI"},{"type":"text","text":", especially large language models (LLMs):"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How LLMs (like ChatGPT) use self-supervised learning"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Task"},{"type":"text","text":": Given a sequence of tokens (words), predict the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"next token"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Labels"},{"type":"text","text":": The true next word is "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"already in the text"},{"type":"text","text":", so no human needs to label it"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Data"},{"type":"text","text":": Massive amounts of raw text (e.g., internet data)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The model learns:"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Language structure - World knowledge - Reasoning patterns - Contextual relationships"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is self-supervised because:\n- The data is "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"unlabeled"},{"type":"text","text":" in the traditional sense\n- The model creates its own “label” by using the next token as the target\n- It then trains as if it were supervised (input → label), but the label is derived from the data"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Similarly:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Image models"},{"type":"text","text":" can be self-supervised by: - Masking parts of an image and predicting the missing parts - Predicting which patches belong together\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Audio models"},{"type":"text","text":" can predict the next frame in a sequence"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"So self-supervised learning is the core training method behind:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"LLMs"},{"type":"text","text":" (GPT, ChatGPT, etc.)\n- Many "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"vision transformers"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Some "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"multimodal models"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Self-supervised learning in Classical Machine Learning"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"In "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"classical machine learning"},{"type":"text","text":", self-supervised learning is "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"less common"},{"type":"text","text":" and not a core paradigm. Classical ML mostly uses:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Supervised learning"},{"type":"text","text":" (labeled data):"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Classification: spam vs. not spam, fraud vs. not fraud - Regression: predict price, temperature, sales\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Unsupervised learning"},{"type":"text","text":" (no labels): - Clustering: K-Means, hierarchical clustering - Dimensionality reduction: PCA, t-SNE"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Self-supervised learning"},{"type":"text","text":" is more of a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"deep learning / neural network"},{"type":"text","text":" technique:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It’s a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"pretraining procedure"},{"type":"text","text":" for neural networks:"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Pretrain on large unlabeled data using self-supervision - Then fine-tune on a smaller labeled dataset for a specific task\n- This is related to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"transfer learning"},{"type":"text","text":": - Instead of pretraining on labeled data, you pretrain on "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"unlabeled data"},{"type":"text","text":" using pretext tasks"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"So in classical ML, self-supervised learning is:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Not a primary paradigm"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- More of an "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"advanced technique"},{"type":"text","text":" used in deep learning to leverage large unlabeled datasets before fine-tuning"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Supervised vs. Unsupervised vs. Self-Supervised"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Aspect"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Supervervised"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Unsupervised"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Self-Supervised"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Labels"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Human-provided labels for each example"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No labels at all"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Labels "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"derived from data itself"},{"type":"text","text":" (no human labels)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Goal"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Predict label from input (classification/regression)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Find patterns, clusters, structure"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn data representations by solving self-generated tasks"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Task type"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"inlineMath","attrs":{"latex":"P(\\text{label} \\mid \\text{input})"}}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Discover structure in "},{"type":"inlineMath","attrs":{"latex":"P(\\text{data})"}}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pretend it’s supervised, but labels are auto-generated"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Data"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Labeled datasets (smaller, expensive)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Unlabeled datasets (large, cheap)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Unlabeled datasets (very large, cheap)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use in classical ML"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dominant (classification, regression)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Used for clustering, dimensionality reduction"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Rare, mostly in deep learning pretraining"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use in Generative AI"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Rare (except for fine-tuning)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Used (GANs, diffusion)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Dominant"},{"type":"text","text":" (LLMs, transformers)"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Self-supervised learning"},{"type":"text","text":" teaches models to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"generate their own labels"},{"type":"text","text":" from unlabeled data and then train as if it were supervised."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"In "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generative AI"},{"type":"text","text":", it’s the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"main training paradigm"},{"type":"text","text":" for LLMs and many deep models: predict the next token, mask-and-reconstruct, etc.."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"In "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"classical ML"},{"type":"text","text":", it’s "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"not a core paradigm"},{"type":"text","text":"; classical ML mostly uses supervised (labeled) and unsupervised (no labels) learning."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Self-supervised learning is a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"pretraining technique"},{"type":"text","text":" for neural networks, related to transfer learning but using unlabeled data."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It enables training on "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"massive unlabeled datasets"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., all internet text) without expensive human annotation."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}}
